<m0>Crushed rock was city's<ql>
<m4>   LINE 1 IS 1.40 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m0>shortcut to boom times<ql>
<m1><ue5><m4>   LINE 2 IS 2.15 PICA(S) SHORT<m2><ql>
<m4>   TOTAL HEAD DEPTH IS .875 INCHES<m2><ql>
